trans-unit.source: Contains values passed to the ASP.NET compiler during precompilation.
trans-unit.target: Contém valores passados para o compilador do ASP.NET durante a pré-compilação.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET Web pages and code files can be precompiled to facilitate a faster response for users and allow for the deployment of the site without deploying the source code.
trans-unit.target: Páginas da Web ASP.NET e arquivos de código podem ser pré-compilados para facilitar uma resposta mais rápida para os usuários e permitir a implantação do site sem implantar o código-fonte.

trans-unit.source: For more information on precompiling an ASP.NET Web site, see [ASP.NET Web Site Project Precompilation Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre pré-compilação de um site ASP.NET, consulte [visão geral de pré-compilação de projeto de Site da Web ASP.NET](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The ClientBuildManagerParameter class stores values that are used during precompilation.
trans-unit.target: A classe ClientBuildManagerParameter armazena valores que são usados durante a pré-compilação.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.PrecompilationFlags%2A> property determines how the assembly will be built.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.PrecompilationFlags%2A>propriedade determina como o assembly será criado.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.PrecompilationFlags%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, you can set <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.PrecompilationFlags%2A> to <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags> to recompile any previously compiled components, or set it to <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags> to permit the resulting assembly to overwrite any components in the target directory.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, você pode definir <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.PrecompilationFlags%2A>para <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags>para recompilar todos os componentes anteriormente compilados ou defina-a como <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags>para permitir que o assembly resultante para substituir todos os componentes no diretório de destino.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.PrecompilationFlags%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags> enumerator has a <xref:System.FlagsAttribute> attribute that allows a bitwise combination of its member values.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags>enumerador tem um <xref:System.FlagsAttribute>atributo que permite uma combinação bit a bit de seus valores de membro.</xref:System.FlagsAttribute> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.PrecompilationFlags%2A> property can contain more than one value from the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags> enumeration to specify a combination of precompilation behaviors.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.PrecompilationFlags%2A>propriedade pode conter mais de um valor da <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags>enumeração para especificar uma combinação dos comportamentos de pré-compilação.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.PrecompilationFlags%2A>

trans-unit.source: Either the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyContainer%2A> property or the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyFile%2A> property is assigned a value to create a strong-named assembly.
trans-unit.target: Tanto o <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyContainer%2A>propriedade ou o <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyFile%2A>propriedade é atribuída um valor para criar um assembly de nome forte.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyFile%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyContainer%2A>

trans-unit.source: Both values do not need to be set to create a strong-named assembly.
trans-unit.target: Ambos os valores não precisam ser definidas para criar um assembly de nome forte.

trans-unit.source: A ClientBuildManagerParameter object is passed to the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager> object through the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Um objeto ClientBuildManagerParameter é passado para o <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager>objeto por meio de <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager.%23ctor%2A>construtor.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager.%23ctor%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManager>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: This constructor does not initialize any property values.
trans-unit.target: Este construtor não inicializar quaisquer valores de propriedade.

trans-unit.source: Those values must be set through the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyContainer%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyFile%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.PrecompilationFlags%2A> properties after the object has been created.
trans-unit.target: Esses valores devem ser definidos por meio de <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyContainer%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyFile%2A>, e <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.PrecompilationFlags%2A>propriedades depois que o objeto foi criado.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.PrecompilationFlags%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyFile%2A> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyContainer%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets excluded virtual paths.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define excluídos caminhos virtuais.

trans-unit.source: Excluded virtual paths.
trans-unit.target: Excluir caminhos virtuais.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the flags that determine precompilation behavior.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define os sinalizadores que determinam o comportamento de pré-compilação.

trans-unit.source: The PrecompilationFlags property determines how the assembly will be built.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade PrecompilationFlags determina como o assembly será criado.

trans-unit.source: For example, you can set PrecompilationFlags to <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags> to recompile any previously compiled components, or set it to <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags> to permit the resulting assembly to overwrite any components in the target directory.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, você pode definir PrecompilationFlags <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags>para recompilar todos os componentes anteriormente compilados ou defina-a como <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags>para permitir que o assembly resultante para substituir todos os componentes no diretório de destino.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags> enumerator has a <xref:System.FlagsAttribute> attribute that allows a bitwise combination of its member values.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags>enumerador tem um <xref:System.FlagsAttribute>atributo que permite uma combinação bit a bit de seus valores de membro.</xref:System.FlagsAttribute> </xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags>

trans-unit.source: The PrecompilationFlags property can contain more than one value from the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags> enumeration to specify a combination of precompilation behaviors.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade PrecompilationFlags pode conter mais de um valor da <xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags>enumeração para especificar uma combinação dos comportamentos de pré-compilação.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags"></xref> for a client build.
trans-unit.target: O <xref href="System.Web.Compilation.PrecompilationFlags"> </xref> para um build do cliente.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the key container used during compilation.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o contêiner de chave usado durante a compilação.

trans-unit.source: Either the StrongNameKeyContainer property or the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyFile%2A> property is assigned a value to create a strong-named assembly.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade StrongNameKeyContainer ou <xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyFile%2A>propriedade é atribuída um valor para criar um assembly de nome forte.</xref:System.Web.Compilation.ClientBuildManagerParameter.StrongNameKeyFile%2A>

trans-unit.source: Both values do not need to be set to create a strong-named assembly.
trans-unit.target: Ambos os valores não precisam ser definidas para criar um assembly de nome forte.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> of the value for the key container.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.String>do valor para o contêiner de chave.</xref:System.String>
